{"tid":1467590,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[非割] 鬼一向都有。捉鬼只係令我地分化。夠多手足，鬼就發揮唔到作用。","createTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:52.000Z","uid":202716,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b5662c97d6bb2e30ea6b301ae430b31e56f69bc6","tid":1467590,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:24:33.000Z","msg":"811 之後，所有焦點去哂捉鬼。<br />\n有鬼有咩出奇?<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">鬼肯撚定一向都有。</span></span><br />\n其實只要夠多人，鬼跟本發揮唔到咩作用!<br />\n佢最多，咪泄露行蹤令狗及早部處。<br />\n但，睇LIVE 都知喇。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鬼，幾時發揮到作用? 就係少人既時候，例如CWB 果次。<br />\n如果多人，鬼唔會捉人。<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">反而，而家手足一齊玩捉鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，就反而令運動失去焦點了。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong><br />\n我明白手足好撚嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但發泄過後，要明白<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">鬼係一定有。但只要手足多過鬼，<br />\n我地一齊黎一齊走。<br />\n鬼就冇佢既價值</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有鬼咪有鬼，驚你?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n異想天開，純粹發夢:  <br />\n反而我諗緊我地有冇可能可以，感化到D鬼，令佢地投誠。<br />\n果陣國民黨好多係共產黨既鬼最尾叛變<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1299ec8688a2c5b117c39148645eddaa3e7eae63","tid":1467590,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:25:09.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"0a588ec1f5637e1caf5990f2f84e9cb87b56f4fd","tid":1467590,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:26:21.000Z","msg":"根本唔駛理鬼"},{"pid":"dfb87354eedea8b40be853d8b78c582fbd6f418b","tid":1467590,"uid":202716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:00.000Z","msg":"PUSH!!!!!!!!!!"},{"pid":"5e0e62e2c760d50f5c3b886d7bcfeb50958c8b61","tid":1467590,"uid":5205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:28:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">必須保護100%和理非行動 <br />\n<br />\n我地可以提早決定100%和理非定 有後續 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警察風向 破壞連登 咩淪陷 唔好信<br />\n<br />\n信左就中警察計<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n和理非 取消黑衫行動 勇武就無左保護 鬼亦無咁多機會滲透<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一定要支持 勇武就無左保護 自然要勇武休息下<br />\n咁鬼既滲透亦無左機會。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但係 講到明有下場既就全民黑衫 （例如免費過海之類）<br />\n<br />\n機場只宣傳 同控制人流 有人搞事就 比泛民 等泛民開記者會<br />\n<br />\n幫手講佢係鬼 <br />\n<br />\n另外唔建議帶口罩 和理非活動係要一家大細都可以參與<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我建議民陣遊行必須 100%和理非 否則就當卧底</span>"},{"pid":"f6d0de387e34dbc47244627bafa027db4e359b17","tid":1467590,"uid":3055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:29:07.000Z","msg":"睇下一直企係我地呢邊既記者，係點睇今晚發生既事<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1467356\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1467356</a>"},{"pid":"9b44448cda6fa2edebfb60a25ebb741610698503","tid":1467590,"uid":162330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T17:34:52.000Z","msg":"手足要注意，勇武都要理性，唔係好打就贏曬"}]}